hy will you continue to rebel?</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_5\">The whole head is sick,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_5\">and the whole heart faint.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_6\"><sup id=\"Isa.1.6\" class=\"v23_1_6\">6</sup>From the sole of the foot even to the head,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_6\">there is no soundness in it,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_6\">but bruises and sores</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_6\">and raw wounds;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_6\">they are not pressed out or bound up</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_6\">or softened with oil.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_7\"><sup id=\"Isa.1.7\" class=\"v23_1_7\">7</sup>Your country lies desolate;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_7\">your cities are burned with fire;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_7\">in your very presence</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_7\">foreigners devour your land;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_7\">it is desolate, as overthrown by foreigners.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_8\"><sup id=\"Isa.1.8\" class=\"v23_1_8\">8</sup>And the daughter of Zion is left</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_8\">like a booth in a vineyard,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_8\">like a lodge in a cucumber field,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_8\">like a besieged city.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_9\"><sup id=\"Isa.1.9\" class=\"v23_1_9\">9</sup>If the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span> of hosts</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_9\">had not left us a few survivors,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_1_9\">we should have been like Sodom,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_1_9\">and become like Gomorrah.</span></p>\n<p class=