g hooks;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_4\">nation shall not lift up sword against nation,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_4\">neither shall they learn war anymore.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_5\"><sup id=\"Isa.2.5\" class=\"v23_2_5\">5</sup>O house of Jacob,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_5\">come, let us walk</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_5\">in the light of the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>.</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">The Day of the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>\n</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_6\"><sup id=\"Isa.2.6\" class=\"v23_2_6\">6</sup>For you have rejected your people,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_6\">the house of Jacob,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_6\">because they are full of things from the east</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_6\">and of fortune-tellers like the Philistines,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_6\">and they strike hands with the children of foreigners.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_7\"><sup id=\"Isa.2.7\" class=\"v23_2_7\">7</sup>Their land is filled with silver and gold,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_7\">and there is no end to their treasures;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_7\">their land is filled with horses,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_7\">and there is no end to their chariots.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_8\"><sup id=\"Isa.2.8\" class=\"v23_2_8\">8</sup>Their land is filled with idols;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_8\">they bow down to the work of their hands,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_8\">to what their own fingers have made.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v23_2_9\"><sup id=\"Isa.2.9\" class=\"v23_2_9\">9</sup>So man is humbled,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v23_2_9\">and each one is brought l