25\"><sup id=\"Isa.7.25\" class=\"v23_7_25\">25</sup>And as for all the hills that used to be hoed with a hoe, you will not come there for fear of briers and thorns, but they will become a place where cattle are let loose and where sheep tread.</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
